Subject: Open Source Martial Arts
Description: Martial artists join in sharing and learning skills with other martial artists! There is much to be learned from practicing with those who study other styles and in other areas. Please bring any source material and equipment you have with you. Come ready to learn and share! Presented by Polaris Fellowship of Weapons Study, a western martial arts school local to Farmington Hills, MI.  Speakers include:Heather Fish, Matthew William, Douglas Scholl, Michael Spagnuolo - Track: Action Adventure  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
